            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1342.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken </strong>to the pan and cook for 5-6 min on each side until golden and crispy and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1342.-step-3-x200.jpg",
