          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with<strong> boiled water </strong>until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and set aside, reserving a cup of <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
