    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> ginger & garlic paste </strong>and <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, the juice of the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>orange </strong>and<strong> </strong>2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> hoisin & orange sauce</strong></p>",
